	<section class="publication js-publication" data-publication-id="3336" data-readtoken="5809bd0cf52e3c61df1098ee" data-publication-type="article" data-is-published="1">

				
		<div class="article-head-container">
	<div class="article-head">
		<div class="article-head-labels">
			


<div class="publication-labels">

	
	<div class="publication-labels-label mod-article-page">
									Oproep
						</div>
</div>
		</div>

		<div class="article-head-metadata">
			<div class="article-head-metadata-data mod-date">
									<time datetime="2015-09-14T09:45" class="article-head-metadata-data mod-date">14 September 2015</time>
							</div>
			
							<div class="article-head-metadata-divider"></div>
				<div class="article-head-metadata-data mod-readingtime">
					
			Leestijd
	
	2
	minuten
				</div>
					</div>

		<div class="article-head-lead" data-field="intro">
			Net als op De Correspondent, is Privacy &amp; Veiligheid ook op ons Festival der Vooruitgang een belangrijk thema. In dit stuk vertel ik wat er op het programma staat.
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="article-head-title" data-field="title">
		Discussieer mee met de baas van de AIVD over de toekomst van onze privacy
	</div>

	<div class="publication-authors  ">
			<div class="publication-authors-department">
			Correspondent Technologie &amp; Surveillance
		</div>
	
	<div class="publication-authors-avatars">
					<div class="publication-authors-avatars-avatar ">
				<img class="publication-authors-avatars-avatar-image" src="https://dynamic.decorrespondent.nl/ff-1433404700/media/380/5570051c9aebb0414642687.png"/>
			</div>
			</div>

	<div class="publication-authors-names">
					<a class="publication-authors-names-name author-name" href="https://decorrespondent.nl/mauritsmartijn">
				<div>
					<span>Maurits</span>
					<span>Martijn</span>
				</div>
			</a>
					
								<div class="publication-authors-names-follow-button js-author-follow is-following" data-author-id="12" data-author-name="Maurits Martijn">
				<div class="publication-authors-names-follow-button-icon"><span class="icon icon-plus"></span></div>
